<br>
Out in t'wilds o Colorado wit a 30.30 o .06 an kill a elk o bull . . . butcher it . . . hang it . . . let it sit fer a day o so, so it donna be tough.<br>
<br>
Then cut yerself a steak. Take a bit o salt an sprinkle it across t'top an pick up t steak. Skake t'steak hard . . . REAL hard so t'not over flaver it too much wit salt.<br>
<br>
Pass it oor t'camp fire a few times wit a fork an plop it down on yer plate. <br>
<br>
Dig in.<br>
<br>
